<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Catálogo Hikvision</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/xlsx/0.18.5/xlsx.full.min.js"></script>
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@supabase/supabase-js@2.39.7/dist/umd/supabase.js"></script>
  <style>
    *,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
    :root{--burg:#800000;--burg-dark:#5a0000;--cream:#f5f5f5;--border:#e0e0e0;--text:#1a1a1a;--text-muted:#888}
    html,body{height:100%}
    body{font-family:"Inter",sans-serif;background:var(--cream);color:var(--text);display:flex;flex-direction:column;overflow:hidden}

    /* ===== LOGIN ===== */
    #login-overlay{position:fixed;inset:0;background:#f0f0f0;z-index:9999;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center}
    .login-card{background:white;border-radius:16px;padding:44px 36px;width:390px;max-width:calc(100vw - 32px);box-shadow:0 8px 48px rgba(0,0,0,.12);text-align:center;border-top:4px solid var(--burg)}
    .login-card img{height:44px;margin:0 auto 20px;display:block}
    .login-card h2{font-size:1rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--burg);margin-bottom:4px}
    .login-card p{font-size:.82rem;color:var(--text-muted);margin-bottom:22px}
    .login-alert{display:none;padding:9px 12px;border-radius:7px;font-size:.82rem;font-weight:500;margin-bottom:12px}
    .login-alert.err{background:#fef2f2;color:#991b1b;border:1px solid #fecaca}
    .login-alert.ok{background:#f0faf4;color:#1a7a3c;border:1px solid #b8e8cc}
    .login-input{width:100%;padding:10px 13px;border:1.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;font-size:.9rem;font-family:inherit;outline:none;margin-bottom:10px}
    .login-input:focus{border-color:var(--burg)}
    .login-btn{width:100%;padding:11px;background:var(--burg);color:white;border:none;border-radius:9px;font-size:.9rem;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;font-family:inherit;margin-bottom:14px}
    .login-btn:hover:not(:disabled){background:var(--burg-dark)}
    .login-btn:disabled{opacity:.55;cursor:not-allowed}
    .login-sep{border:none;border-top:1px solid #eee;margin:4px 0 14px}
    .guest-btn{width:100%;padding:9px;background:transparent;color:#888;border:1px solid #ddd;border-radius:9px;font-size:.82rem;cursor:pointer;font-family:inherit}
    .guest-btn:hover{border-color:var(--burg);color:var(--burg)}

    /* ===== ROLE PILLS ===== */
    .role-pill{font-size:.7rem;font-weight:700;padding:2px 9px;border-radius:20px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.08em;flex-shrink:0}
    .role-diamond{background:#dbeafe;color:#1d4ed8}.role-black{background:#1a1a1a;color:#fff}
    .role-platino{background:#ede9fe;color:#6d28d9}.role-ruby{background:#ffe4e6;color:#be123c}
    .role-gold{background:#fef3c7;color:#92400e}.role-guest{background:#f3f4f6;color:#6b7280}

    /* ===== HEADER ===== */
    .header{background:#fff;padding:10px 32px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;position:sticky;top:0;z-index:100;box-shadow:0 3px 12px rgba(0,0,0,.10);border-bottom:2px solid var(--burg);flex-shrink:0}
    .logo-wrapper{display:flex;align-items:center}
    .header-title{color:var(--burg);font-weight:700;font-size:.9rem;letter-spacing:.15em;text-transform:uppercase;position:absolute;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%)}
    .header-right{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px}
    .usr-badge{font-size:.75rem;color:#666;max-width:180px;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis;white-space:nowrap}
    .logout-btn{display:none;padding:5px 12px;background:white;border:1px solid #ddd;border-radius:6px;font-size:.78rem;cursor:pointer;color:#666}
    .logout-btn:hover{border-color:var(--burg);color:var(--burg)}
    .rt-badge{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;font-size:.72rem;color:#555;padding:4px 10px;border-radius:20px;border:1px solid var(--border);background:#fafafa}
    .rt-badge.connected{color:#1a7a3c;border-color:#b8e8cc;background:#f0faf4}
    .rt-badge.connecting{color:#a07010;border-color:#f0d890;background:#fffbec}
    .rt-badge.disconnected{color:#cc3333;border-color:#f5c0c0;background:#fff5f5}
    .rt-dot{width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;background:#ccc;flex-shrink:0}
    .rt-badge.connected .rt-dot{background:#1a7a3c}
    .rt-badge.connecting .rt-dot{background:#c09020}
    .rt-badge.disconnected .rt-dot{background:#cc3333}

    /* ===== TOAST ===== */
    .toast-container{position:fixed;bottom:24px;right:24px;z-index:9999;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px;pointer-events:none}
    .toast{padding:10px 16px;border-radius:8px;font-size:.82rem;font-weight:500;color:white;background:#1a7a3c;box-shadow:0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,.2);transform:translateX(120%);transition:transform .3s;pointer-events:none}
    .toast.show{transform:translateX(0)}
    .toast.update{background:#1a5a9a}.toast.error{background:#8a2020}

    /* ===== TOOLBAR – 2 rows ===== */
    .toolbar{background:white;padding:8px 32px 6px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);flex-shrink:0;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:6px}
    .toolbar-row{display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap}

    /* Search */
    .search-wrap{flex:0 0 28%;position:relative;min-width:180px}
    .search-icon{position:absolute;left:12px;top:50%;transform:translateY(-50%);color:var(--text-muted)}
    .search-spinner{position:absolute;right:10px;top:50%;transform:translateY(-50%);display:none}
    .search-spinner.active{display:block}
    .search-input{width:100%;padding:9px 36px 9px 38px;font-size:.88rem;font-family:inherit;border:1.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:6px;outline:none;background:#fafafa}
    .search-input:focus{border-color:var(--burg);background:white}

    /* Checkboxes dropdowns */
    .cb-dropdown{position:relative;flex:1;min-width:120px}
    .cb-dropdown-btn{width:100%;padding:9px 30px 9px 12px;border:1.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:6px;font-size:.82rem;font-family:inherit;cursor:pointer;background:#fafafa;text-align:left;white-space:nowrap;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis}
    .cb-dropdown-btn:hover{border-color:var(--burg)}
    .cb-dropdown-panel{display:none;position:absolute;top:calc(100% + 2px);left:0;min-width:100%;max-width:300px;background:white;border:1.5px solid var(--burg);border-radius:6px;z-index:300}
    .cb-dropdown-panel.open{display:block}
    .cb-panel-search{padding:8px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
    .cb-panel-search input{width:100%;padding:5px 9px;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:5px;font-size:.82rem}
    .cb-panel-list{max-height:220px;overflow-y:auto;padding:4px 0}
    .cb-panel-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:6px 12px;cursor:pointer;font-size:.84rem}
    .cb-panel-item:hover{background:#fdf0f0}
    .cb-panel-item input[type="checkbox"]{accent-color:var(--burg);width:14px;height:14px}
    .cb-panel-footer{padding:5px 12px 7px;border-top:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;justify-content:space-between}
    .cb-count-label{font-size:.75rem;color:var(--text-muted)}
    .cb-clear-btn{font-size:.78rem;color:var(--burg);background:none;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-weight:700}

    /* ===== VIEW TOGGLE ===== */
    .view-toggle{display:flex;background:#f0f0f0;border-radius:7px;padding:2px;flex-shrink:0}
    .view-btn{padding:6px 14px;border:none;border-radius:5px;background:transparent;cursor:pointer;font-size:.8rem;font-weight:600;font-family:inherit;color:#666;transition:all .15s;white-space:nowrap}
    .view-btn.active{background:white;color:var(--burg);box-shadow:0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,.12)}
    .view-btn:not(.active):hover{color:var(--burg)}

    /* ===== PRICE TOGGLE BUTTONS ===== */
    .price-toggles{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;flex-shrink:0}
    .price-toggles-label{font-size:.72rem;font-weight:700;color:#888;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.08em;white-space:nowrap}
    .price-btn{padding:6px 13px;border:1.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:6px;background:white;cursor:pointer;font-size:.8rem;font-weight:600;font-family:inherit;color:#666;transition:all .15s;white-space:nowrap;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px}
    .price-btn:hover{border-color:#aaa;color:#333}
    .price-btn .dot{width:7px;height:7px;border-radius:50%;background:currentColor;opacity:.4;transition:opacity .15s}
    .price-btn.active .dot{opacity:1}

    /* Propio = azul */
    .price-btn.propio.active{background:#dbeafe;color:#1d4ed8;border-color:#93c5fd}
    /* Canal = verde */
    .price-btn.canal.active{background:#d1fae5;color:#065f46;border-color:#6ee7b7}
    /* ML = amarillo */
    .price-btn.ml.active{background:#fef3c7;color:#92400e;border-color:#fcd34d}

    .price-btn:disabled{opacity:.35;cursor:not-allowed}

    /* Export */
    .btn-green{padding:7px 14px;font-size:.82rem;font-weight:700;border-radius:6px;cursor:pointer;border:none;background:#1a7a3c;color:white;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;white-space:nowrap;flex-shrink:0}
    .btn-green:hover{background:#145c2c}
    .btn-admin{display:none !important;}

    /* ===== STATUS BAR ===== */
    .status-bar{padding:3px 32px;background:#fff8f8;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);min-height:22px;flex-shrink:0}
    .loading-bar{display:none;align-items:center;gap:8px;color:var(--burg);font-size:.83rem;font-weight:500}
    .loading-bar.active{display:flex}
    .spinner{width:14px;height:14px;border:2.5px solid #f0d0d0;border-top-color:var(--burg);border-radius:50%;animation:spin .7s linear infinite}
    @keyframes spin{to{transform:rotate(360deg)}}

    /* ===== MAIN / TABLE ===== */
    main{padding:10px 32px 6px;overflow-x:auto;flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;min-height:0}
    .card{background:white;border-radius:10px;box-shadow:0 2px 16px rgba(0,0,0,.08);overflow:hidden;display:flex;flex-direction:column;flex:1;min-height:0}
    .tbl-wrap{overflow-x:auto;overflow-y:auto;width:100%;flex:1;min-height:0}
    .tbl-head,.tbl-row{display:flex;flex-direction:row;align-items:stretch;width:100%}
    .tbl-head{background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--burg-dark),var(--burg));position:sticky;top:0;z-index:10}
    .tbl-row{border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);max-height:60px;overflow:hidden}
    .tbl-row:nth-child(even){background:#fafafa}
    .tbl-row:hover{background:#fff0f0}

    /* Price cells */
    .price{font-weight:700!important;font-size:.82rem;text-align:center}
    .p-diamond{color:#2b7fd4}.p-plat{color:#7070a0}.p-ruby{color:#be123c}
    .p-gold{color:#b8860b}.p-goldplus{color:#c07000}.p-map{color:#065f46}
    .p-zero{color:#ccc;font-weight:400!important}

    /* Pagination */
    .pagination{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:6px;padding:7px;background:white;border-top:1px solid var(--border);flex-wrap:wrap;flex-shrink:0}
    .page-btn{padding:5px 11px;border:1.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:5px;background:white;cursor:pointer;font-size:.83rem}
    .page-btn:hover,.page-btn.active{background:var(--burg);color:white;border-color:var(--burg)}
    .page-btn:disabled{opacity:.3;cursor:not-allowed}
    .page-info{color:var(--text-muted);font-size:.82rem}

    /* Lightbox */
    .lightbox{display:none;position:fixed;inset:0;background:rgba(0,0,0,.85);z-index:1000;align-items:center;justify-content:center}
    .lightbox.active{display:flex}
    .lightbox img{max-width:70vw;max-height:70vh;object-fit:contain;border-radius:10px}
    .lightbox-close{position:absolute;top:18px;right:24px;color:white;font-size:2.2rem;cursor:pointer}

    /* Image cell */
    .img-cell{flex:0 0 56px!important;width:56px!important;min-width:56px!important;max-width:56px!important;height:56px!important;max-height:56px!important;display:flex!important;align-items:center!important;justify-content:center!important;padding:4px!important;border-right:1px solid #f0f0f0;overflow:hidden!important;position:relative;flex-shrink:0!important}
    .img-thumb{display:block!important;width:48px!important;height:48px!important;max-width:48px!important;max-height:48px!important;min-width:0!important;min-height:0!important;object-fit:contain!important;flex-shrink:1!important;border-radius:4px;border:1px solid #eee;background:#fff;cursor:pointer}
    .img-placeholder{width:48px;height:48px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;border-radius:4px;border:1px dashed #ddd;background:#fafafa;color:#ccc;font-size:.55rem;text-align:center;line-height:1.2;flex-shrink:0}
    .func-cell{display:-webkit-box;-webkit-line-clamp:2;-webkit-box-orient:vertical;overflow:hidden;line-height:1.5;font-size:.73rem;word-break:break-word;overflow-wrap:break-word;color:#333;cursor:default;}

    /* ===== SUMMARY VIEW BADGE ===== */
    .view-badge{display:none;align-items:center;gap:6px;padding:3px 32px;background:#fffbec;border-bottom:1px solid #fcd34d;font-size:.78rem;color:#92400e;font-weight:500;flex-shrink:0}
    .view-badge.active{display:flex}

    /* ===== ADMIN IMPORT MODAL ===== */
    .modal-overlay{display:none;position:fixed;inset:0;background:rgba(0,0,0,.6);z-index:2000;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:16px}
    .modal-overlay.active{display:flex}
    .modal-box{background:white;border-radius:14px;width:900px;max-width:100%;max-height:90vh;display:flex;flex-direction:column;box-shadow:0 20px 80px rgba(0,0,0,.35);border-top:4px solid #1a3a6a}
    .modal-header{padding:18px 24px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;flex-shrink:0}
    .modal-header h2{font-size:1rem;font-weight:700;color:#1a3a6a;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px}
    .modal-close{background:none;border:none;font-size:1.6rem;cursor:pointer;color:#aaa;line-height:1}
    .modal-close:hover{color:#333}
    .modal-body{padding:20px 24px;overflow-y:auto;flex:1}
    .modal-footer{padding:14px 24px;border-top:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;justify-content:flex-end;gap:10px;flex-shrink:0}
    .import-step{margin-bottom:20px}
    .import-step h3{font-size:.82rem;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.08em;color:#1a3a6a;margin-bottom:10px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px}
    .step-num{width:20px;height:20px;background:#1a3a6a;color:white;border-radius:50%;font-size:.7rem;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0}
    .import-info{background:#eff6ff;border:1px solid #bfdbfe;border-radius:8px;padding:12px 14px;font-size:.8rem;color:#1e40af;line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:14px}
    .import-info code{background:#dbeafe;padding:1px 5px;border-radius:3px;font-family:monospace;font-size:.78rem}
    .drop-zone{border:2px dashed #cbd5e1;border-radius:10px;padding:28px;text-align:center;cursor:pointer;transition:all .2s;background:#f8fafc}
    .drop-zone:hover,.drop-zone.dragover{border-color:#1a3a6a;background:#eff6ff}
    .drop-zone p{font-size:.85rem;color:#64748b;margin-bottom:6px}
    .drop-zone small{font-size:.75rem;color:#94a3b8}
    .drop-zone input[type=file]{display:none}
    .col-map-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr;gap:10px;margin-top:10px}
    .col-map-item{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:4px}
    .col-map-item label{font-size:.75rem;font-weight:600;color:#475569}
    .col-map-item select{padding:7px 10px;border:1.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:6px;font-size:.82rem;font-family:inherit;outline:none}
    .col-map-item select:focus{border-color:#1a3a6a}
    .preview-wrap{max-height:220px;overflow:auto;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px}
    .preview-table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:.75rem}
    .preview-table th{background:#1a3a6a;color:white;padding:7px 10px;text-align:left;font-weight:600;position:sticky;top:0}
    .preview-table td{padding:6px 10px;border-bottom:1px solid #f0f0f0;max-width:220px;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis;white-space:nowrap}
    .preview-table tr:nth-child(even) td{background:#f8fafc}
    .preview-table tr:hover td{background:#eff6ff}
    .preview-stats{display:flex;gap:16px;margin-bottom:10px;flex-wrap:wrap}
    .stat-pill{padding:5px 12px;border-radius:20px;font-size:.75rem;font-weight:600}
    .stat-total{background:#dbeafe;color:#1d4ed8}.stat-foto{background:#d1fae5;color:#065f46}
    .stat-func{background:#fef3c7;color:#92400e}.stat-skip{background:#fee2e2;color:#991b1b}
    .progress-bar-wrap{background:#e2e8f0;border-radius:20px;height:8px;overflow:hidden;margin-top:8px}
    .progress-bar-fill{height:100%;background:#1a3a6a;border-radius:20px;transition:width .3s}
    .progress-label{font-size:.75rem;color:#64748b;margin-top:4px}
    .btn-primary{padding:9px 20px;background:#1a3a6a;color:white;border:none;border-radius:7px;font-size:.85rem;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;font-family:inherit}
    .btn-primary:hover{background:#122a50}
    .btn-primary:disabled{opacity:.5;cursor:not-allowed}
    .btn-secondary{padding:9px 20px;background:white;color:#666;border:1.5px solid #ddd;border-radius:7px;font-size:.85rem;cursor:pointer;font-family:inherit}
    .btn-secondary:hover{border-color:#1a3a6a;color:#1a3a6a}
    .import-log{background:#0f172a;color:#94a3b8;border-radius:8px;padding:12px;font-size:.72rem;font-family:monospace;max-height:140px;overflow-y:auto;margin-top:12px;display:none}
    .import-log.active{display:block}
    .log-ok{color:#4ade80}.log-err{color:#f87171}.log-info{color:#93c5fd}
    .field-check{display:flex;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:8px}
    .field-check label{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;font-size:.82rem;cursor:pointer}
    .field-check input[type=checkbox]{accent-color:#1a3a6a;width:15px;height:15px}
    .warn-box{background:#fffbeb;border:1px solid #fcd34d;border-radius:7px;padding:10px 14px;font-size:.78rem;color:#92400e;margin-top:10px;display:none}
    .warn-box.active{display:block}
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ===== LOGIN OVERLAY ===== -->
<div id="login-overlay">
  <div class="login-card">
    <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dmmj4nmxp/image/upload/v1771907606/Captura_de_pantalla_2026-02-23_232840_m1jg3p.png" alt="Hikvision" onerror="this.style.display='none'" />
    <h2>Catálogo de Productos</h2>
    <p>Iniciá sesión para ver tus precios</p>
    <div id="login-alert" class="login-alert"></div>
    <input id="login-email" class="login-input" type="email" placeholder="Email" autocomplete="email" />
    <input id="login-pass" class="login-input" type="password" placeholder="Contraseña" autocomplete="current-password" />
    <button id="btn-login" class="login-btn">Ingresar</button>
    <hr class="login-sep" />
    <button id="btn-guest" class="guest-btn">Continuar como invitado (solo precios MAP)</button>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ===== ADMIN IMPORT MODAL ===== -->
<div class="modal-overlay" id="import-modal">
  <div class="modal-box">
    <div class="modal-header">
      <h2>
        <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4"/><polyline points="17 8 12 3 7 8"/><line x1="12" y1="3" x2="12" y2="15"/></svg>
        Importar fotos y funciones desde Excel / CSV
      </h2>
      <button class="modal-close" id="modal-close-btn">&times;</button>
    </div>
    <div class="modal-body">
      <div class="import-step">
        <h3><span class="step-num">1</span> Formato del archivo</h3>
        <div class="import-info">
          El archivo Excel o CSV debe tener al menos una columna <strong>SAP</strong> y las columnas que quieras importar:<br>
          &nbsp;• <code>foto</code> — URL completa de la imagen en Cloudinary<br>
          &nbsp;• <code>funciones</code> — Descripción funcional del producto<br><br>
          También acepta nombres alternativos: <code>sap_code</code>, <code>sap code</code>, <code>cod_sap</code>, <code>functional description</code>, <code>descripcion</code>, <code>image_url</code>, <code>cloudinary_url</code>
        </div>
        <div class="field-check">
          <label><input type="checkbox" id="chk-foto" checked /> Actualizar <strong>foto</strong></label>
          <label><input type="checkbox" id="chk-func" checked /> Actualizar <strong>funciones</strong></label>
          <label><input type="checkbox" id="chk-overwrite" /> Sobreescribir campos que ya tienen datos</label>
        </div>
        <div class="warn-box" id="warn-overwrite">
          ⚠️ Con "Sobreescribir" activado, se reemplazarán los datos existentes en la base.
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="import-step">
        <h3><span class="step-num">2</span> Seleccioná el archivo</h3>
        <div class="drop-zone" id="drop-zone">
          <input type="file" id="file-input" accept=".xlsx,.xls,.csv" />
          <p>📂 Arrastrá un archivo aquí o <strong>hacé clic</strong> para seleccionar</p>
          <small>Formatos soportados: .xlsx · .xls · .csv</small>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="import-step" id="step-map" style="display:none">
